  "notes": [
    "This clinical practice guideline provides evidence-based recommendations for diagnosis and treatment of primary adrenal insufficiency",
    "The short corticotropin test is identified as the gold standard diagnostic tool",
    "Treatment recommendations include specific dosing for fludrocortisone and hydrocortisone/cortisone acetate",
    "The guideline emphasizes monitoring for associated autoimmune diseases, particularly thyroid disease"
